{"analytics_identifier":"OT495","base_path":"/government/organisations/defence-equipment-and-support","content_id":"73833cda-22ca-4711-87f9-73a98814315d","description":"As an arm’s length body of the Ministry of Defence, we deliver equipment and support services to the Royal Navy, British Army, and Royal Air Force. DE&S is an executive agency, sponsored by the Ministry of Defence .","details":{"acronym":"DE&S","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>As an arm’s length body of the Ministry of Defence, we deliver equipment and support services to the Royal Navy, British Army, and Royal Air Force.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Defence Equipment and Support\">DE&amp;S</abbr> is an executive agency, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence\">Ministry of Defence</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-defence","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Defence Equipment &amp; Support","image":{"alt_text":"Defence Equipment and Support","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67cea2aeade26736dbfa00b0/DES_LOGO2024_COLOUR_.png"}},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/defence-equipment-and-support-des-organisation-chart-2023","title":"Our organisation chart"},{"href":"/government/organisations/defence-equipment-and-support/about/recruitment","title":"Working for DE&S"},{"href":"https://des.mod.uk/careers/vacancies/","title":"Jobs"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/des-drive-successful-ajax-cold-weather-trials","image":{"alt_text":"Ajax on the Rangers during testing in extreme weather conditions in Sweden. MOD Crown Copyright 2024.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65facf6b9316f5001d64c3de/s712_resized_ajaz.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65facf6baa9b76001dfbdba6/s465_resized_ajaz.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65facf6b9316f5001164c3c2/resized_ajaz.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2024-03-06T16:11:50.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Members of the DE&amp;S Ajax delivery team worked with the British Army Household Cavalry Regiment (HCR) to put Ajax through its paces in sub-zero temperatures in Sweden.</p>\n</div>","title":"DE&S drive successful Ajax cold weather trials"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/new-des-non-executive-directors-announced","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6464b1970b72d3001334460f/s712_ministry-of-defence-building.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6464b1970b72d3000c344605/s465_ministry-of-defence-building.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6464b1970b72d3000c344604/ministry-of-defence-building.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2023-05-17T11:46:21.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>DE&amp;S has welcomed two new Non-Executive Directors to the DE&amp;S Board.</p>\n</div>","title":"New DE&S Non-Executive Directors announced"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/161-million-contract-for-f-35-jet-maintenance-supports-140-uk-jobs","image":{"alt_text":"F-35 jet","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/642ea3937de82b0012313750/s712_17.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/642ea393fbe620000c17dded/s465_17.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/642ea393ddf8ad000cac0f03/17.png"},"public_updated_at":"2023-04-04T00:15:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The UK’s fleet of F-35 Lightning stealth jets will be maintained and supported in a new £161 million contract, keeping them ready for global combat operations</p>\n</div>","title":"£161 million contract for F-35 jet maintenance supports 140 UK jobs"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/hms-birmingham-steel-cut-milestone-supports-thousands-of-uk-jobs","image":{"alt_text":"HMS Birmingham steel cut","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/642ea3cefbe620000f17dde7/s712_16.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/642ea3ceddf8ad0013ac0f13/s465_16.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/642ea3cefbe620000c17ddef/16.png"},"public_updated_at":"2023-04-04T12:16:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Steel has been cut on the first of the second batch of Type 26 warships, following a £4.2 billion contract awarded to BAE Systems in November 2022.</p>\n</div>","title":"HMS Birmingham steel cut milestone supports thousands of UK jobs"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/5t-uncrewed-ground-vehicles-gives-glimpse-of-future-battlefield","image":{"alt_text":"Elbit Robust","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/642ea420fbe620000f17dde9/s712_Gov.uk-4.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/642ea420fbe620000f17ddea/s465_Gov.uk-4.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/642ea420ddf8ad0013ac0f14/Gov.uk-4.png"},"public_updated_at":"2023-03-31T09:30:16.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The first ever UK trial of heavy uncrewed ground systems (H-UGVs) has taken place, testing their effectiveness in battlefield situations.</p>\n</div>","title":"5T+ uncrewed ground vehicles gives glimpse of future battlefield"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/can-robot-dogs-programmed-with-ai-find-hidden-explosive-devices","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65562c74046ed400148b9a4e/s712_IMG_9169__1_.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65562c74046ed4000d8b9a52/s465_IMG_9169__1_.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65562c74d03a8d001207fa9d/IMG_9169__1_.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2023-11-16T14:25:57.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Forty programmers demonstrated how AI-enabled robotic dogs could carry out potentially dangerous tasks that would otherwise be undertaken by Army bomb disposal experts at the Defence AI Centre (DAIC) sponsored Hackathon on 7 to 9 November.  </p>\n</div>","title":"Can robot dogs programmed with AI find hidden explosive devices?"}],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://des.mod.uk/careers/","title":"Careers at DE&S"},{"href":"https://des.mod.uk/careers/graduate-schemes-and-apprenticeships/","title":"Apprentices and graduates "},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/desider-magazine","title":"Read Desider magazine "}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"executive_agency","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/company/defence-equipment-support/","service_type":"linkedin","title":"LinkedIn"},{"href":"https://twitter.com/DefenceES","service_type":"twitter","title":"Twitter"},{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/DefenceES/","service_type":"facebook","title":"Facebook"},{"href":"https://www.instagram.com/defence_equipment_support/","service_type":"instagram","title":"Instagram"},{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKc8rCBhCkF6lWMNnCmMsag","service_type":"youtube","title":"YouTube"}]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-12-06T11:40:18+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT495","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/defence-equipment-and-support","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/defence-equipment-and-support","base_path":"/government/organisations/defence-equipment-and-support","content_id":"73833cda-22ca-4711-87f9-73a98814315d","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-04-01T07:58:14Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Defence Equipment and Support","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/defence-equipment-and-support","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/andy-start","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/andy-start","base_path":"/government/people/andy-start","content_id":"49b4b705-ff00-4c59-9399-be72d61d3858","details":{"image":null,"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"11a8e15f-f56f-4bad-b74b-44e00f11b217","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2025-10-13T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2025-03-31T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"62630c76-6461-4745-82de-eebb27d55244","details":{"body":"<p>Leads the National Armaments Director (<abbr title=\"National Armaments Director\">NAD</abbr>) Group, bringing together the teams responsible for developing, delivering, sustaining, housing and harbouring the UK’s ‘national arsenal’ and defence estate.</p>\n\n<p>Responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>delivering the capabilities required from industry to execute the defence plans and operations demanded by the new era</li>\n  <li>shaping and delivering the Defence Industrial Strategy</li>\n  <li>ensuring a resilient supply chain and the required readiness of the ‘national arsenal’</li>\n  <li>leading on UK defence exports and acquisition reform</li>\n  <li>harmonising procurement and working closely with wider government, industry, academia, and international partners to deploy best practice and investment</li>\n  <li>managing safety, risk and environmental issues in accordance with mandated requirements and appropriate best practice</li>\n  <li>representing UK interests in international military and political fora, including NATO and the EU</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/groups/national-armaments-director-nad-group\">National Armaments Director (<abbr title=\"National Armaments Director\">NAD</abbr>) Group</a></p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-17T15:26:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"National Armaments Director (NAD)","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-13T11:34:13Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Andy Start - National Armaments Director (NAD)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"4c6a69b7-cb59-47b9-a7e2-9fa87fa6ee8e","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":8089,"started_on":"2022-09-05T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"40c926b5-88af-4903-ab0b-7f357ac8b75a","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Executive Officer is the UK’s National Armaments Director and as the Accounting Officer for Defence Equipment and Support (<abbr title=\"Defence Equipment and Support\">DE&amp;S</abbr>) is directly responsible to Parliament for the stewardship of <abbr title=\"Defence Equipment and Support\">DE&amp;S</abbr>’ resources.</p>\n\n<p>To discharge these responsibilities, CEO has delegated authority from PUS to lead and manage <abbr title=\"Defence Equipment and Support\">DE&amp;S</abbr>:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>providing equipment and logistic support to current operations, including delivery against urgent operational requirements</li>\n  <li>delivering funded equipment acquisition and support outputs, as agreed with Front Line Commands and the Head Office</li>\n  <li>delivering projects to performance, time and cost targets, in accordance with agreed asset delivery plans</li>\n  <li>managing safety, risk and environmental issues in accordance with mandated requirements and appropriate best practice</li>\n  <li>representing UK interests in international military and political fora, including NATO and the EU</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-03-31T14:44:05Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Executive of Defence Equipment and Support (DE&S)","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-09-28T09:16:03Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Andy Start - Chief Executive of Defence Equipment and Support (DE&S)","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-13T11:38:18Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Andy Start","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/andy-start","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_contacts":[{"content_id":"d46c2975-0a90-434c-a637-6780ed24d6bd","details":{"contact_form_links":[{"link":"https://des.mod.uk/contact-us/"}],"description":null,"email_addresses":null,"phone_numbers":null,"post_addresses":[{"iso2_country_code":"gb","locality":"Bristol","postal_code":"BS34 8JH","street_address":"Ministry of Defence\r\nDE&S Secretariat\r\nMaple 0a, #2043\r\nMOD Abbey Wood","world_location":"United Kingdom"}],"title":"Head Office"},"document_type":"contact","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-03-21T14:34:39Z","schema_name":"contact","title":"Head Office","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"a9e8ec1b-3c0d-4e4e-9f6a-0193c5ea8a3a","details":{"contact_form_links":null,"description":"If you have a complaint about DE&S, please contact us at  the address above.","email_addresses":[{"email":"dessec-parliamentarybusiness@mod.gov.uk","title":"DE&S Secretariat"}],"phone_numbers":null,"post_addresses":[{"iso2_country_code":"gb","locality":"Bristol","postal_code":"BS34 8JH","street_address":"Maple 0a, #2043, MOD Abbey Wood","title":"DE&S Secretariat","world_location":"United Kingdom"}],"title":"How to complain"},"document_type":"contact","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-03-31T14:35:32Z","schema_name":"contact","title":"How to complain","withdrawn":false},